Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz352.9\fs40\pos(825.4,691)}電波誠譯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 叮咚  - 媽\N{\fs38}- Ding dong. - Hey, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ellie 奶奶到了 她帶你去上學\N{\fs38}Ellie! Grandma's here! She's gonna take you to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先別說話 是的 我今天要穿這件夾克\N{\fs38}And before you say anything, yes, I'm wearing this jacket today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那行吧 這是什么顏色 灰褐色嗎 \N{\fs38}Oh, if you say so. What is that, taupe?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 這是英國軍隊的卡其色\N{\fs38}No, it's British military khaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擺出那副嘴臉了\N{\fs38}and stop making that face because...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會換衣服的\N{\fs38}I'm not changing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你干什么 你現在那表情又是什么意思\N{\fs38}What? What are you... what are you pointing that face at now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么啊 我就站在這兒\N{\fs38}Nothing. I'm just standing here being a person,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著臟兮兮的廚房\N{\fs38}looking at a filthy kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ellie昨晚應該洗盤子的\N{\fs38}Ellie was supposed to do the dishes last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她肯定后來睡覺去了\N{\fs38}but she must have fallen asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 您還真是紀律嚴明呢\N{\fs38}Tight ship you're running, leftenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會整天聽你叨叨的\N{\fs38}Well, I'm not hearing that all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 鋪床了嗎  - 如果你不去我房間看 那我就鋪了\N{\fs38}- Did you make your bed? - If you don't open my door, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思我睡過頭了 我們昨晚熬夜看了<西區故事>(歌舞片)\N{\fs38}Sorry I overslept. We stayed up late watching Westside Story,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到兇手跳完舞才睡\N{\fs38}and didn't get to bed until after the dance murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你擊中了\N{\fs38}Oh, you got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sean Harrison早間表演 謝謝\N{\fs38}Thank you. The Sean Harrison breakfast players.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我要用下你的信用卡\N{\fs38}By the way, I need your credit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周末出去玩 要租一個滑雪板\N{\fs38}card to rent a snowboard for my trip this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 去拿吧 錢包在樓上  - 周末出去玩\N{\fs38}- Yeah, my wallet's upstairs. - Weekend trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ellie和她朋友第一次去滑雪噢\N{\fs38}Ellie and some friends are going snowboarding for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.81,0:01:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太激動了\N{\fs38}I'm so excited! 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.70,0:01:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶 她遺傳了你的叫聲\N{\fs38}Oh, my God, she has your scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.82,0:01:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她睡過頭了 不干家務\N{\fs38}So she oversleeps, doesn't do her chores,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不但不禁足她 還給她信用卡\N{\fs38}and instead of grounding her, you give her a credit card?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.49,0:01:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該去給芝加哥的懶漢做現場解說\N{\fs38}You should do play-by-play for the Chicago bummers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就說說 她不把你當回事兒\N{\fs38}I'm just saying, she doesn't take you seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.46,0:01:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可把我當回事兒了\N{\fs38}She takes me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.95,0:01:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是嫉妒我是一個有趣的家長\N{\fs38}You're just jealous because I'm fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你呢\N{\fs38}whereas you withheld
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不按字母順序整理好調味架 你就不讓我出去\N{\fs38}approval if I didn't alphabetize the spice rack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可喜歡了\N{\fs38}Oh, you loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實喜歡\N{\fs38}Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也可以對Ellie很嚴厲的 相信我\N{\fs38}But I can be plenty tough on Ellie if I have to be. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 你得馬上把這些盤子洗了\N{\fs38}Honey, I need you to do these dishes now, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 但是我上學要遲到了  - 確實是 你走吧\N{\fs38}- But I'll be late for school. - That's valid. Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你軟得跟嬰兒屁股一樣\N{\fs38}You're as soft as a baby's bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ellie 等下\N{\fs38}Ellie, hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里的事情你也得多上點心\N{\fs38}You're gonna have to chip in more around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便吧 晚飯見\N{\fs38}Whatever. I'll see you at dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這句話應該我對你說 因為今晚你來做飯\N{\fs38}No, I'll see you at dinner, because tonight you're gonna cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不做 周末就別想出去玩兒了\N{\fs38}And if you don't, you don't get to go on your trip this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 太扯了吧\N{\fs38}What? That's insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確扯 但就這樣了 因為我說了算\N{\fs38}That is insane, but it's happening now because I just said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行吧 我先上車\N{\fs38}Fine, I'll be in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 你那件新的灰褐色夾克純屬裝逼失敗\N{\fs38}Oh, and your new taupe jacket is trying too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是英國軍隊的卡其色\N{\fs38}It's British military khaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了嗎\N{\fs38}Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我態度強硬得很(我是個強受)\N{\fs38}I am one bad-ass bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 說出來就不對勁了\N{\fs38}That, um... that came out wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣你都會讓她出去玩兒的\N{\fs38}You're never gonna take that trip away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這對她太重要了 最后肯定是這樣\N{\fs38}It's too important to her. Here's what's gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她今晚沒有做飯 但你還是不會怪她\N{\fs38}There'll be no meal tonight, but you'll let her go anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候她就知道你耳根子到底有多軟了\N{\fs38}and then she'll know what a pushover you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是強忍著才沒把你掛到陽臺外頭\N{\fs38}I am trying so hard not to dangle you off the balcony right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ellie今晚如果沒做飯\N{\fs38}So, either Ellie's gonna cook dinner tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就別想去滑雪了\N{\fs38}or she doesn't get to go on her ski trip this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能演壞警察啊 又不是沒演過\N{\fs38}I can be bad cop. I've done it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某一類派對上\N{\fs38}At certain costume parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那確實是很"壞"的警察\N{\fs38}Okay, that was naughty cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果你禁足Ellie 你也得在家呆著了\N{\fs38}But if you ground Ellie you're gonna have to stay in town,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是要去Courtney的婚禮嗎\N{\fs38}and we're supposed to go to Courtney's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶 我都忘了是這周了\N{\fs38}Oh, my God, I forgot that's this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的需要你陪我去啊 她是我的老朋友了\N{\fs38}I need you there. She's my oldest friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我有多討厭她\N{\fs38}You know how much I hate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么突然開始對Ellie這么嚴厲了\N{\fs38}How did you pick now to go all tough on Ellie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是被我媽逼的\N{\fs38}Because my Mom made me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她說得很對\N{\fs38}But she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ellie應該多管管家里的事兒 做做飯\N{\fs38}Ellie should pitch in more, make some meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她得知道 不是只要你餓了\N{\fs38}She has to learn that food just
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物就這么神奇地出現了\N{\fs38}doesn't magically appear every time you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你的午餐  - 謝天謝地\N{\fs38}- Your lunch is here. - Oh, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我餓死了 謝謝你Stavros \N{\fs38}I'm starving. Thank you, Stavros.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 28.50美金  - 好的\N{\fs38}- $28.50. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我未來的女朋友Liz 你好\N{\fs38}Hello, my future girlfriend, Liz.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的 Stavros\N{\fs38}It's not happening, Stavros.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得不可能而已 對我來說早就開始了\N{\fs38}For you. For me it has already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是"周末爸爸"的時候\N{\fs38}Things were so much less
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有這么多壓力\N{\fs38}stressful with Ellie when I was the weekend Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 我得換些零錢\N{\fs38}Here. I need some change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sean 你做得很棒 Ellie很愛你\N{\fs38}You're doing fine, Sean. Ellie loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 但我希望她能一直這么喜歡我\N{\fs38}I know, but I want her to keep
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我禁足她 她會恨我的\N{\fs38}liking me and if I ground her, she'll hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教育孩子又不是拼人氣\N{\fs38}Parenting is not a popularity contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要給孩子們立好規矩\N{\fs38}Children need boundaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕還有別的人需要規矩\N{\fs38}They're not the only ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說我就認識一個送外賣的\N{\fs38}For instance, I know a certain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為自己是家庭心理咨詢師\N{\fs38}delivery guy who thinks he's a family therapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.04,0:04:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Liz 我們要對我們的孩子更加嚴厲一點\N{\fs38}Liz, we will be more firm with our children.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我們會有分歧 但我們永遠不會把怒氣帶上床\N{\fs38}Yes, we will argue, but we will never go to bed angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sean 周五我能不能早點下班\N{\fs38}Hey, Sean, I was hoping I could skip out early on Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的樂隊有個史上最大的演出\N{\fs38}Our band's got our biggest gig ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 活兒留給我們 去追逐你的夢想吧\N{\fs38}Sure, we'll cover for you. Follow your dreams, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不會飛 還算什么鳥\N{\fs38}Can't be a bird if you don't fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥\N{\fs38}Ostrich.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧鴕鳥確實不會飛 總之 你可以提前走\N{\fs38}Okay ostriches don't fly, but the point is you can leave early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 謝謝 Sean  - 沒什么\N{\fs38}- Thanks, Sean. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞 火雞 企鵝\N{\fs38}Chicken, turkey, penguin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sean 借一步說話\N{\fs38}Sean, a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sean 我聽到你要讓Hunter提前走\N{\fs38}Sean, I overheard you giving Hunter time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆大家都像法國人一樣中午就走了\N{\fs38}Why don't we all just skip out at noon like the French
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用剩下的時間吃小三明治 搞外遇\N{\fs38}and spend our days having tiny sandwiches and affairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是在諷刺 可是聽上去好棒\N{\fs38}I know you're being sarcastic, but that sounds amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sean 作為你的導師\N{\fs38}Sean, as your mentor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 導師  - 不客氣\N{\fs38}- Mentor? - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來教你兩招\N{\fs38}I'm going to give you a piece
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何讓你的雇員更加高效\N{\fs38}of advice to make your employees more productive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能再那樣溺愛他們了\N{\fs38}You have got to stop coddling them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始攪亂他們的頭腦\N{\fs38}and start messing with their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們失去平衡 疑神疑鬼\N{\fs38}Keep them off balance and paranoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在考慮要不要炒你的魷魚\N{\fs38}I'm thinking about firing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不會的 是嗎 你可不知道\N{\fs38}No, I'm not. Am I? You don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Max 你玩心理戰術 是不能激發他們的潛力的\N{\fs38}Max, you don't get the best out of people by playing mind games.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要以誠待人 循循引導\N{\fs38}You have to be honest and encouraging
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我假想的父親 <天臺風云>里的Tim Gunn\N{\fs38}like my imaginary Father, Tim Gunn, on Project Runway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來某人想和我打個賭啊\N{\fs38}It sounds to me like someone would like to wager.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么就像要打賭了\N{\fs38}How does that sound like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就賭\N{\fs38}You're on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打賭 我能讓Hunter\N{\fs38}I will bet you that I can
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自愿放棄他那寶貴的演出機會\N{\fs38}get Hunter to voluntarily skip his precious gig
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求我讓他整個周末都加班\N{\fs38}and beg me to work all weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓這個賭更有意思\N{\fs38}And just to make it more interesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還會讓他往你身上扔一個你心愛的松餅\N{\fs38}I will even get him to throw one of your beloved muffins at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是你的松餅了\N{\fs38}Um, let's call that your muffin now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我可不想把Hunter\N{\fs38}And I don't wanna treat Hunter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當成實驗室的小白鼠一樣\N{\fs38}like a lab rat in some deranged experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 這事兒我來干 \N{\fs38}Oh, goody. That'll be my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以來定賭注\N{\fs38}You may set the terms of the wager.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fs38}All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你輸了 那就讓Hunter去演出\N{\fs38}If you fail and Hunter goes to his gig,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你還得對辦公室的每個人說句好聽的話\N{\fs38}then you have to say one nice thing to everyone in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 真險惡\N{\fs38}Oh, ha ha! Fiendish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我贏了 你就得對每個人說句難聽的話\N{\fs38}And if I succeed, you must tell one mean truth to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個都不能告訴Hunter\N{\fs38}And neither one of us can tell
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就沒有意思了\N{\fs38}Hunter what we're doing, that would spoil the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思\N{\fs38}What fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fs38}Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思 這事兒啊 多么有意思\N{\fs38}What fun... we will have... when we do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hunter\N{\fs38}Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大H H炸彈 在這兒呢\N{\fs38}Big H. The H-bomb. There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道Sean讓你提前下班\N{\fs38}I understand that Sean gave you some time off
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追逐你的音樂夢想\N{\fs38} to pursue your musical dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 這沒什么問題吧 Max  - 當然沒問題\N{\fs38}- I hope that's okay, Max. - Oh, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想太重要了\N{\fs38}Dreams are important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如你今天也別上班了 好好休息吧\N{\fs38}In fact, why don't you take the rest of today off as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么呢\N{\fs38}Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sean一直都在和我說\N{\fs38}Well... Sean's been telling
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的音樂對你來說有多重要\N{\fs38}me how important your music is to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你有足夠的時間來準備你的演出\N{\fs38}I want you to have plenty of time to prepare,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.19,0:06:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以快回去吧 寫一首像<We Built This City>這樣的\N{\fs38}so go and write the next "We Built This City".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你從來不讓人提前走的啊 Max\N{\fs38}But you never want people to leave early, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 Sean已經說服我了\N{\fs38}Oh, no, but Sean has convinced me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要像一只美麗的夜鶯一樣自由地飛翔\N{\fs38}that you need to fly free like a beautiful songbird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧 走吧 不要回頭\N{\fs38}So go. Go and don't look back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了不要回頭\N{\fs38}I said don't look back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:07:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我剝開你的頭骨 啃噬你的心\N{\fs38}Oh, I shall peel back your skull and snack on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽 你在這兒干嘛呢\N{\fs38}Hey, Mom, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過來看看Ellie有沒有做晚飯 看來她沒做\N{\fs38}I came by to see if Ellie had made dinner. It appears she hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好我包里有救急卷餅\N{\fs38}Thank God I have an emergency burrito in my purse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ellie 下來\N{\fs38}Ellie, come down here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先別急著下定論\N{\fs38}Let's not jump to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許她會捧著一個大火腿下來呢\N{\fs38}Maybe she'll walk down the stairs carrying a giant ham.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你現在陷入了一個怎樣的泥潭嗎\N{\fs38}You see how you've boxed yourself in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不讓她去滑雪 她就沒轍了\N{\fs38}You take away her trip, she'll be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你退縮了 她就知道她能隨心所欲了\N{\fs38}If you back down, she'll know she can do whatever she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后她鼻子上的環會比浴簾上還要多\N{\fs38}She'll end up with more rings in her nose than a shower curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 奶奶 我知道要做晚飯了 馬上\N{\fs38}Hi, Dad. Hi, Grandma. I know, dinnertime. I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝天謝地 看到了嗎\N{\fs38}Oh, thank God. You see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有責任感的好孩子 我完美的孩子\N{\fs38}My responsible child. My perfect child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Julia Child(美國名廚)\N{\fs38}My Julia Child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那兒瞎操心\N{\fs38}And you were worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我一直都知道 她會迎難而上\N{\fs38}But I knew all along she would rise to the challenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,付出努力 給我們做一頓美味的 自制的\N{\fs38}put the effort in, and make us a delicious, homemade...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟 她在用湯罐頭蒙混過關 \N{\fs38}Oh, crap, she's half-assing it with a can of soup, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂\N{\fs38}Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:07:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湯妹\N{\fs38}Soupie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎么了  - 親愛的 抱歉\N{\fs38}- Yes? - Honey, I'm sorry, okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開一罐爸爸留給感冒或者宿醉的湯\N{\fs38}but opening a can of Daddy's special flu and hangover soup
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不算是做晚飯啊\N{\fs38}does not count as making dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以\N{\fs38}Oh! And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了結她\N{\fs38}Finish her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的周末滑雪之旅\N{\fs38}I'm afraid your weekend trip is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 等下 你又沒告訴我這些規則\N{\fs38}No, no, no, wait. No. You didn't tell me the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我應該要做一頓大餐\N{\fs38}I didn't know I was supposed to make some big, fancy meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得對 她說得對\N{\fs38}You're right! She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能因為她不知道這些規則就罰她\N{\fs38}You can't punish someone who didn't know the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在新加坡嚼口香糖\N{\fs38}That's how I got out of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是用的這個理由逃過了鞭刑\N{\fs38}getting caned for chewing gum in Singapore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 再給你一次機會 明晚如果你不好好做一頓飯\N{\fs38}Okay, one more chance. Tomorrow night, if you don't make a dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就別想去滑雪了\N{\fs38}that takes some effort, your trip is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很公平 因為我才發現\N{\fs38}Fair enough. Because I just realized
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一罐燴番茄\N{\fs38}this is a can of stewed tomatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我知道 她搞砸了 但是我又沒告訴她規則\N{\fs38}I know, I know, she blew it, but I didn't tell her the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是對的 你說得對\N{\fs38}You're right, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她自己應該能想到的 但是我對她太嚴厲了\N{\fs38}She should have figured it out, but I was tough on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能沒那么嚴厲\N{\fs38}Okay, maybe not that tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果明晚\N{\fs38}But if she doesn't make dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7:30她還沒做飯 那就別怪我不客氣 別想去玩兒了\N{\fs38}tomorrow night by 7:30 sharp, that's it, no trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信我嗎 明天親自過來瞧瞧\N{\fs38}You don't believe me? Come tomorrow and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 還有事嗎\N{\fs38}What? Something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經說得夠多了\N{\fs38}I've said too much already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"致Hunter Max上"\N{\fs38}"To Hunter from Max"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Max為什么要給我一盒松餅粉\N{\fs38}Why would Max leave me a box of muffin mix?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開看看\N{\fs38}Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許里頭有個戒指呢\N{\fs38}Maybe there's a ring inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sean\N{\fs38}Sean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Max在我桌上放了盒松餅粉\N{\fs38}Max left me a box of muffin mix on my desk,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天他還要我提前回去了\N{\fs38}then he sent me home early yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在搞什么鬼啊 我是不是現在要給他做松餅\N{\fs38}What the hell's going on? Am I supposed to make him muffins now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能告訴你 總之不要亂想\N{\fs38}I cannot tell you. Just don't get paranoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 所以確實有什么事情  - 我不能這么說\N{\fs38}- So something is going on? - I cannot say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 但是你就這么說了  - 我不能說\N{\fs38}- But you did say that. - I cannot say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 發生什么了  - 好吧\N{\fs38}- What's happening? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你很愛音樂\N{\fs38}Look, I know how much you love music,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周五安心去演出就好了\N{\fs38}so go to your gig on Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.64,0:09:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不管怎樣 不要沖我扔松餅\N{\fs38}But whatever you do, do not throw a muffin at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什么要沖你扔松餅\N{\fs38}Why would I throw a muffin at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能說\N{\fs38}I cannot say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收到你的郵件了\N{\fs38}I got your email.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說如果Ellie今晚沒做晚飯\N{\fs38}What do you mean if Ellie doesn't cook dinner tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就要禁足她\N{\fs38}you're gonna have to ground her
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她一起待在家里\N{\fs38}stay at home with her this weekend
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去婚禮了 是什么意思\N{\fs38}and miss the wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪里不懂\N{\fs38}What part didn't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我寫得最清楚的一封郵件了\N{\fs38}Because it's arguably the clearest email I've ever written.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂\N{\fs38}Oh, I understood it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果我只身一人去參加Courtney的婚禮\N{\fs38}But if I have to go to Courtney's wedding without a date,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就會上了新郎 把婚禮蛋糕當帽子戴在頭上\N{\fs38}I'm going to screw the groom, wear the wedding cake as a hat,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在照相亭里懸梁自盡\N{\fs38}and hang myself in the photo booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張照片肯定很搞笑\N{\fs38}That's gonna be a funny picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣嘛 我需要你的幫助\N{\fs38}Now, come on. I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你裝作是Ellie 讓我練習練習如何變得嚴厲\N{\fs38}Pretend to be Ellie so I can practice being tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我干嘛要幫你\N{\fs38}Why should I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是朋友\N{\fs38}Because you're my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是作為朋友的分內事\N{\fs38}and that's what friends do for each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 Sean\N{\fs38}All right, Sean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我幫你 那我就幫\N{\fs38}You want my help, you got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在的小姑娘都心狠嘴毒\N{\fs38}But teenage girls can be savages.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會留情面的 你有心理準備嗎\N{\fs38}They fight dirty. You ready for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別廢話了 趕緊的\N{\fs38}Enough trash talk. Let's just do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 我回來了 晚飯怎么沒做啊\N{\fs38}Hi, honey, I'm home, and I don't see any dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了 但是我給了無家可歸的人了\N{\fs38}I made it, but then I gave
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才是更需要的人啊\N{\fs38}it to a homeless person who needs it more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.18,0:10:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有本事你證明我說謊啊\N{\fs38}Prove I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:11:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她 她 她不會這么說的\N{\fs38}She... she... she wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這才剛開始熱身呢 再來\N{\fs38}Oh, I'm just getting warmed up. Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 我回來了 晚飯沒做 不許你去旅游\N{\fs38}Hi, honey, I'm home and I don't see any dinner, so no trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 你扯什么淡\N{\fs38}That's a bag of crap, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個大肥淡\N{\fs38}You're a big, fat bag of crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦 她比我記憶中要兇狠很多嘛 我接著演\N{\fs38}Wow, she's a lot more hostile than I remember, but, I'll play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 親愛的 我知道你很生氣\N{\fs38}Okay, honey, I know you're mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我氣媽媽去紐約工作\N{\fs38}Yeah, I'm mad because my Mom took a job in New York
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻選擇留下來陪你 我現在腸子都悔青了\N{\fs38}and I chose to stay here with you, and I totally regret it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你滿腦子都是各種破規矩\N{\fs38}because all you care about are your stupid rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不理解我\N{\fs38}and you don't understand me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你還要罰我\N{\fs38}And now you have to punish me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是奶奶的走狗\N{\fs38}because you're Grandma's little bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 你想哭了嗎 老爸現在是要哭了嗎\N{\fs38}Oh, what's the matter? You gonna cry? Daddy gonna cry now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶 是啊 \N{\fs38}Oh, my God. Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦 如果她像你這么說話 我就死了\N{\fs38}Wow! If she says any of that, I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就不要冒這個險了 和我去參加婚禮 會玩得很開心的\N{\fs38}Well, then why risk it? Come to the wedding, we'll have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 記住 你是來給我精神支持的\N{\fs38}Okay, remember, you're here for moral support,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要為了讓我陪你去婚禮\N{\fs38}not to talk me into letting
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就哄我放她一馬\N{\fs38}Ellie slide so I can go to the wedding with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 精神支持 "請攜親友"不就是派這用場的嘛 Sean\N{\fs38}Got it. Moral support. That's what "Plus ones" do, Sean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你厲害\N{\fs38}Way to keep swinging.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聞到了\N{\fs38}I smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣 我什么都沒聞到\N{\fs38}Nothing. I smell nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信 她又沒做晚飯\N{\fs38}I can't believe this. She didn't make dinner again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ellie\N{\fs38}Ellie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 可能烤箱里會有東西\N{\fs38}Wait! Maybe there's something in the oven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ellie\N{\fs38}Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 這燉菜看著就好吃\N{\fs38}Oh, look. A beautiful casserole.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你這戲準備怎么演  - 烤到一半\N{\fs38}- And your plan is... - Half-baked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了她這個虛擬的燉菜我已經盡力了\N{\fs38}Which is more than I can say for her pretend casserole.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶 我現在只能當壞警察了\N{\fs38}Damn it! Now I have to be bad cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她為什么要把我逼到這地步\N{\fs38}Why does she put me in this position?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 出了點急事\N{\fs38}Sorry, there was an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sarah和她媽媽大吵了一架\N{\fs38}Sarah got into this huge fight with her Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很難過 我沒法留她一個人在那兒\N{\fs38}She was super-upset. I couldn't just leave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Ellie 我們說好的  - 我知道 是我不對\N{\fs38}- Ellie, we had a deal. - I know, and I blew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在做錯事了 所以不許你出去旅游\N{\fs38}And you blew it, so you may not go on your trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我明白  - 不管你怎么反抗\N{\fs38}- I understand. - No matter how much you fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我沒想反抗  - 或者把責任推給你的朋友Sarah\N{\fs38}- I'm not fighting you. - Or blame it on your friend Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不怪Sarah  - 你不能\N{\fs38}- I'm not blaming Sarah. - You may not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去旅游嗎 我知道\N{\fs38}Go on my trip? I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你找了很多借口\N{\fs38}I gave you plenty of chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sean\N{\fs38}Sean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像情況有點特別\N{\fs38}I think something's happening here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像Ellie是在 承擔責任\N{\fs38}I think Ellie's... taking responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不說 El 換我可不會這么輕易認錯的\N{\fs38}I gotta say, El, this is not how I would have played it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我出了什么事\N{\fs38}Tell me what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sarah總是偷懶不做家務\N{\fs38}Sarah's always getting out of doing her chores,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的父母每次都會生氣 然后他們就會吵架\N{\fs38}and her parents are always mad and fighting with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望我們也這樣\N{\fs38}I just don't want us to be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我做錯了 \N{\fs38}I blew it, so I'm just gonna
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就接受懲罰 爭取下次不再犯咯\N{\fs38}accept my punishment and try not to screw up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶 我女兒最懂事了\N{\fs38}Oh, my God, you're a fantastic child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想做一個好相處的爸爸 但你一犯懶\N{\fs38}I wanna be fun Dad, but when you slack off,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就會變成很兇的爸爸 就像個\N{\fs38}I turn into harsh Dad, which makes me feel like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 讓你失望了 老爸  - 是啊 "讓人失望的老爸"\N{\fs38}- Sorry, Dad. - Yes! "Sorry Dad".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就變成猛灌咖啡酒和伏特加的老爸\N{\fs38}Who then turns into Kahlua and vodka Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是說對不起\N{\fs38}No, I meant I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以后會主動做家務的 我保證\N{\fs38}I'll do more without you having to bug me. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fs38}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你周末去玩吧\N{\fs38}You can go on your trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么 真的嗎  - 是的 因為我相信你\N{\fs38}- What? Really? - Yes. Because I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fs38}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這周末都能出去玩啦\N{\fs38}We all get to go away this weekend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 我們出去吃飯慶祝一下 我那份飯錢我自己付\N{\fs38}Come on, let's go out and celebrate. My part of dinner's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 等一下 等一下 我們不能走 我媽正趕過來呢\N{\fs38}Wait, wait, wait. We can't go out. My Mom's coming over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被她發現你沒做晚飯\N{\fs38}If she sees that you didn't cook dinner and I
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我沒有關你禁閉 我要被她嘮叨一輩子\N{\fs38}didn't ground you, I'll never hear the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得對 就算你死了都不會放過你\N{\fs38}You're right. Even after you're dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會寫張條子然后塞進你的棺材\N{\fs38}she's gonna write a note and slip it in your casket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.07,0:14:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我覺得她會活得比你久\N{\fs38}And, yes, I think she's going to outlive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.78,0:14:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 我們點街轉角的那家希臘菜 \N{\fs38}All right, we'll order Greek food
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說是你做的\N{\fs38}from the place on the corner and say you made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉串 米飯色拉 這些你自己也能做的 對吧\N{\fs38}Shish kebab, rice salad... you can make those things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果自動出現在門口 我能\N{\fs38}If they show up at the door, I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩天前你那"一定行"的精神去哪兒了\N{\fs38}Where was that "Can do" Attitude two days ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我給你做了啥\N{\fs38}Look what I made for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松餅 給我的\N{\fs38}Muffins. For me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦\N{\fs38}You betcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好大的膽子\N{\fs38}How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這反應倒是出人意料啊\N{\fs38}That... right there is an unexpected reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你給我松餅粉就是為了\N{\fs38}I assumed that when you gave me the muffin mix, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會給你什么松餅粉\N{\fs38}I did not give you muffin mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭松餅 我奶奶就是因為松餅過世的\N{\fs38}I hate muffins. Muffins killed my Grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 松餅怎么了  - 她在面包店工作\N{\fs38}- They what now? - She worked at a bakery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:15:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她往桶里倒藍莓的時候沒有站穩\N{\fs38}She was adding blueberries to the vat, and she lost her footing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人說去世時不痛苦是件幸福的事情 但是\N{\fs38}They say a better death is a peaceful death, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把這話去跟一個肺里\N{\fs38}Try telling that to an old woman whose lungs
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是藍莓和酵母的老人家說看看\N{\fs38}are filling with blueberries and yeast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是盒子上有張紙條說是你送的啊 Max\N{\fs38}But there was a note on the box that said it was from you, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好一個栽贓嫁禍\N{\fs38}A clever forgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明顯 有人想設法讓你惹惱我\N{\fs38}Obviously, someone is trying to get you to offend me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指望我炒你魷魚\N{\fs38}perhaps so that I will fire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炒我魷魚\N{\fs38}Fire me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過誰會想讓你被炒魷魚呢\N{\fs38}Oh, no, but who would want to get you fired, and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 還有誰會知道我悲傷的蛋糕故事 沒人知道啊\N{\fs38}who would know about my tragic muffin history? Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了Sean\N{\fs38}Except Sean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不可能是Sean  - 不 不 不會 不會\N{\fs38}- It couldn't be Sean. - No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很喜歡你 雖然\N{\fs38}He loves you. Although...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然什么\N{\fs38}Although what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 不 不 不 不可能是Sean\N{\fs38}No, no, no, no, no! Couldn't be Sean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 雖然  - 什么啊\N{\fs38}- Although... - What!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的確說過要讓你自由地飛翔\N{\fs38}Well, he does keep saying that you've got to fly free
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追逐音樂夢想\N{\fs38}and pursue your musical dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能覺得 只有逼你跳出鳥巢\N{\fs38}Maybe he thinks the only way that you'll do that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才會下定決心去追逐夢想\N{\fs38}is if you're forced out of the nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不想離開這兒\N{\fs38}But I don't want to leave the nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想你離開\N{\fs38}And I don't want you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但顯然 Sean想\N{\fs38}But clearly... Sean does.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sean錯了 我愛這兒\N{\fs38}Well, Sean is wrong! I love the nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兒有醫保還能拿到商品的七五折\N{\fs38}The nest has health care and 25% off returned merchandise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 但是就像Sean說的 你遠遠高于這個地方\N{\fs38}I know, but like Sean says, you are better than this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我和這里完全平等\N{\fs38}No, I am not. I'm exactly equal to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 去你的表演  - 你不能強迫我\N{\fs38}- Go to your gig! - You can't make me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪兒也不去\N{\fs38}I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我要留下然后工作一整個周末\N{\fs38}In fact, I'm gonna stay here and work all weekend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fs38}Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 把這些小松餅拿走\N{\fs38}Now, get these muffins out of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sean在我們倆中作梗實在讓我氣得想\N{\fs38}I'm so mad at Sean for manipulating both of us, I might just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沖他丟個松餅 一定很有快感 但\N{\fs38}throw one at him, which would be enormously satisfying. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 這不是我的戰爭  - 這不是你的 是我的\N{\fs38}- it's not my fight. - No, it is not. It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住\N{\fs38}Remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不住在玻璃房子里的人 是扔松餅的\N{\fs38}People who don't live in glass houses do throw muffins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs38}出自諺語Those who live in a glass house shouldn't throw stones.住在玻璃房子里的人不應該扔石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話有理\N{\fs38}It makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 現在廚房看起來像用過的了\N{\fs38}Okay. Now the kitchen looks like a meal's been made.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快 穿過去\N{\fs38}Okay, quick, walk through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 Calvin Klein的烹飪謊言\N{\fs38}Ah! Culinary lies by Calvin Klein.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 進來 - 送餐\N{\fs38}- Come in! - Delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 Stavros 進來 快點\N{\fs38}Oh, Stavros, my man, come in here, quick, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把這些東西弄到盤子上\N{\fs38}I gotta get this stuff on plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我媽十分鐘內就到了\N{\fs38}My Mom gets here in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好 Sean 漂亮的Liz 任性的女兒\N{\fs38}Hello, Sean, beautiful Liz, unruly daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任性 你和別人說我什么了\N{\fs38}Unruly? What do you tell people about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專注在你的工作上就好了 拜托\N{\fs38}Just focus on your job, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是希臘經濟倒臺的原因\N{\fs38}This is why the Greek economy's falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,52.5美元\N{\fs38}$52.50.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 給你\N{\fs38}Great. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門怎么是開的\N{\fs38}Why is the door open?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽 你來早了\N{\fs38}Mom! You're early.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 大伙兒 好消息 媽來早了\N{\fs38}Hey, everybody, great news... Mom's early!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊 這是誰\N{\fs38}Ooh. Something smells good. Who's this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是 呃\N{\fs38}This? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Stavros\N{\fs38}This is Stavros.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希臘人\N{\fs38}He is Greek.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么在這兒\N{\fs38}Uh huh. And why is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為\N{\fs38}Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是Liz的男友\N{\fs38}He's Liz's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔啪(希臘人常用嘆詞) 大家都開心了\N{\fs38}Opa! We're all happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 唔啪 - 唔啪\N{\fs38}- Opa! - Opa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 他是我男友\N{\fs38}True! He's my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別打他主意哦 Lorna\N{\fs38}Hands off, Lorna!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托Stavros的福 Ellie做了一頓希臘大餐\N{\fs38}Ellie made this Greek feast in Stavros's honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 都是我一個人做的 - 很棒嘛 親愛的\N{\fs38}- All by myself. - Well, wonderful, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stavros 你和Liz交往多久了\N{\fs38}So, Stavros, how long have you and Liz been dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這周四就滿六周了\N{\fs38}Six weeks this Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她之前鞋跟卡在下水道上的橫欄里了\N{\fs38}She got her heel caught in a sewer grate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救了她一命 然后現在\N{\fs38}I saved her life and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.36,0:18:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們成了情人\N{\fs38}We are lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這頓飯是為了犒勞Stavros的勇敢\N{\fs38}While this dinner was to honor Stavros for his bravery,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不幸的是 他得走了\N{\fs38}unfortunately, he has to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能留下的\N{\fs38}I can stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Liz 過來\N{\fs38}Liz, woman, come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想念你的愛撫\N{\fs38}I miss your touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 Stavros\N{\fs38}Oh, Stavros!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真好\N{\fs38}You're so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡看你穿吊帶衫的時候\N{\fs38}I love it when you wear tank tops
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶子迷失在你肩發中的樣子\N{\fs38}and the straps get all lost in your shoulder hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你是干什么的 Stavros\N{\fs38}So... what do you do, Stavros?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是家庭心理咨詢師\N{\fs38}I am a family therapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心理咨詢師 哇\N{\fs38}A therapist? Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你會對一個\N{\fs38}So what would you say to a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.75,0:18:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從不想管教自己女兒的爸爸說什么呢\N{\fs38}Father who never wants to discipline his daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你會對一個以為自己\N{\fs38}And what would you say to a Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無比了解怎么當家長的媽媽說什么\N{\fs38}who thinks she knows everything about parenting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你會對一個\N{\fs38}And what would you say
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女兒不做晚餐又不禁她足\N{\fs38}to a man whose daughter doesn't cook dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒叫了希臘菜外賣\N{\fs38}but instead of grounding her because he can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想裝作是自家做的菜的男人說什么\N{\fs38}orders Greek food and tries to pass it off as homemade?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會說 你該把手臂放下來了\N{\fs38}I'd say it all means it's time for you to get your arm off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我付錢送你出門\N{\fs38}And for me to pay you and send you on your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只后悔點的不是中餐\N{\fs38}My only regret is I didn't order Chinese food,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ping Li會演好這出戲的\N{\fs38}because Ping Li would have nailed this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Liz 我們可以在蜜月的時候回味這件事\N{\fs38}Liz, we will laugh about this on our honeymoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 所以Ellie確實搞砸了\N{\fs38}Okay, so Ellie did screw up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她承擔了責任 我為她驕傲\N{\fs38}but she took responsibility, and I'm proud of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但按原計劃 你要禁她足\N{\fs38}But the deal was you were supposed to ground her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 計劃是 她是我的女兒\N{\fs38}No, the deal is she's my daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做我認為對的事\N{\fs38}and I have to do what feels right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且目前為止 計劃很有效 因為她是個很好的孩子\N{\fs38}And so far, it's working, because she's a great kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜怎么著 我不會禁她足\N{\fs38}So guess what. I'm not grounding her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要禁你足\N{\fs38}I'm grounding you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么  - 你聽見了\N{\fs38}- What? - You heard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個禮拜都不能給我建議\N{\fs38}You cannot give me advice for one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不公平 我不知道規則\N{\fs38}That's not fair. I didn't know the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你說什么 你想要兩個禮拜\N{\fs38}What? What was that? You wanna go for two weeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便了\N{\fs38}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:20:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你說什么  - 好吧\N{\fs38}- Excuse me? - Okay, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個禮拜之內都不會再提出任何意見\N{\fs38}I will not voice an opinion about anything for one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 開動吧\N{\fs38}Excellent! Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ellie辛苦了一天 雖然不是為了這個\N{\fs38}Ellie slaved all day not making this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請期待不是我做的甜點吧\N{\fs38}Wait till you see what I didn't make for dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這周末的準備你做好了嗎\N{\fs38}Are you all set for this weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶上舞鞋了嗎\N{\fs38}Did you pack your dancing shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我一直穿著呢\N{\fs38}Uh... I'm never not wearing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能跟我來我太開心了\N{\fs38}I'm so happy you're coming with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可以開心地在那些單身妹子面前跳舞\N{\fs38}Now dancing to all the single ladies
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是在旁邊一邊看一邊腹誹了\N{\fs38}will be fun instead of just a pointed observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 不 Hunter 我說過了不管你干什么\N{\fs38}Oh, no. Hunter, I said whatever you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.18,0:20:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都別沖我扔松餅\N{\fs38}do not throw a muffin at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就不該\N{\fs38}Then maybe you shouldn't have
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我松餅粉 還讓我覺得那是Max送的\N{\fs38}given me that muffin mix and made me think that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好讓我因為向他提起\N{\fs38}it was from Max so that I would get fired for reminding him
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他祖母悲劇的死而被炒魷魚\N{\fs38}of his Grandmother's tragic batter death!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 Max真是厲害\N{\fs38}Wow, Max has been busy.
